# Digital Wall Management System

A full-stack web application for an outdoor advertising marketplace platform connecting wall owners and advertisers.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> A valid `RAZORPAY_KEY_ID` and `RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET` will be needed in the `.env` file to fully test the payment integration. For testing without real keys, I will configure the app to bypass verification if keys are not provided, or I can use dummy test keys for UI demo.
> Similarly, a valid MongoDB connection string is required. I will use a local MongoDB instance (`mongodb://localhost:27017/dwms`) by default. Please ensure MongoDB is running locally or provide a remote URI.

## Proposed Changes

### Backend Setup
#### [NEW] backend/package.json
Dependencies: express, mongoose, bcrypt, jsonwebtoken, dotenv, cors, razorpay, multer (for images).
#### [NEW] backend/server.js
Setup express app, connect to MongoDB, setup route prefixes.
#### [NEW] backend/models/User.js
User schema with role (advertiser, owner, admin) and auth details.
#### [NEW] backend/models/Wall.js
Wall schema (title, type, location, pricing, images, owner, status, daily traffic).
#### [NEW] backend/models/Booking.js
Booking schema (advertiser, wall, dates, pricing breakdown, status, razorpay_order_id).

### Backend Controllers & Routes
#### [NEW] backend/controllers/authController.js
Register and login logic.
#### [NEW] backend/routes/authRoutes.js
Auth endpoints.
#### [NEW] backend/controllers/wallController.js
Wall CRUD, approval by admin, public listing.
#### [NEW] backend/routes/wallRoutes.js
Wall endpoints.
#### [NEW] backend/controllers/bookingController.js
Booking creation, Razorpay order generation, payment verification, CPM calculations.
#### [NEW] backend/routes/bookingRoutes.js
Booking endpoints.

### Frontend Setup
#### [NEW] frontend/package.json
React (Vite), react-router-dom, axios, tailwindcss (if requested, else plain css). *Note: Instruction says "Vanilla CSS for maximum flexibility and control. Avoid using TailwindCSS unless the USER explicitly requests it". I will use vanilla CSS.*
#### [NEW] frontend/index.html & frontend/src/main.jsx
Entry points.
#### [NEW] frontend/src/index.css
Global styles containing the required outdoor advertising theme (brick wall background, concrete cards, LED glow).

### Frontend Components & Pages
#### [NEW] frontend/src/components/Navbar.jsx
Responsive navbar.
#### [NEW] frontend/src/pages/Home.jsx
Wall listings with poster overlay previews.
#### [NEW] frontend/src/pages/Login.jsx & Register.jsx
Auth pages.
#### [NEW] frontend/src/pages/WallDetail.jsx
Wall details, CPM calculator, smart price calculator, and booking/checkout UI.
#### [NEW] frontend/src/pages/AdvertiserDashboard.jsx
Active/past campaigns, spend, ROI.
#### [NEW] frontend/src/pages/OwnerDashboard.jsx
Manage walls, view earnings.
#### [NEW] frontend/src/pages/AdminDashboard.jsx
Wall approvals, analytics.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Build verification for both backend and frontend.

### Manual Verification
- Start backend and frontend servers.
- Register Admin, Owner, Advertiser users.
- Owner creates walls.
- Admin approves walls.
- Advertiser browses and books a wall (testing Razorpay flow and price calculations).
- Verify dashboard data for all three roles.
